ernational dance moves of a high-intensity Zumba class with the specific needs of people who prefer to sit to exercise.";i:34;s:151:"Aug 10 2013 - Zumba Chair exercises can provide a beneficial cardio workout to individuals who are unable to tolerate a more rigorous form of exercise.";i:35;s:93:"When autocomplete results are available use up and down arrows to review and enter to select.";i:36;s:59:"Touch device users explore by touch or with swipe gestures.";i:37;s:25:"Zumba Sentao Perfect For.";i:38;s:51:"People who want to get some serious core work done.";i:39;s:42:"Pull up a chair and tone your entire body.";i:40;s:119:"Zumba Sentao combines strength and resistance training with innovative dance moves using a chair as your dance partner.";i:41;s:145:"A high intensity workout that focuses on defining your muscles improving overall cardiovascular health and burning major calories in the process.";i:42;s:17:"Out with the old.";i:43;s:113:"There is a whole new meaning to Zumba now and it involves using a chair to strengthen and tone your core muscles.";i:44;s:62:"While it still includes many of the Latin-infused dance moves.";i:45;s:179:"Yoga Chair Exercises Stretching Exercises Spinal Cord Injury Senior Fitness Aerobics Physical Education Zumba Excercise Wheelchair seated Zumba - On the Floor - Jennifer Lopez ft.";i:46;s:155:"Pitbull Instructor - Christina ClarkeParticipant - Mary Fashik who has Cerebral PalsyFilmed at YMCA of Golden Isles GAI do not own the rights to this song.";i:47;s:59:"Other ways to get a good workout are gentler on the joints.";i:48;s:133:"If you have a handicap or other physical limitation consider wheelchair Zumba classes which are a good fun nonweight-bearing workout.";i:49;s:75:"Im a licensed Zumba instructor and I teach wheelchair Zumba online on Zoom.";i:50;s:79:"This class focuses on upper body movements including shoulders arms chest neck.";i:51;s:53:"Able body participants are more than welcome to join.";i:52;s:33:"Its a great workout for everyone.";i:53;s:61:"Its 8 per class and payments can be made via Venmo or PayPal.";i:54;s:139:"Classes offer a modified version of the classic Zumba that recreates the original movesat a lower intensity according to the Zumba website.";i:55;s:162:"A slow song that gradually speeds up like Proud Mary was a favorite among residents at Southfork a DePaul Senior Living Community in Winston-Salem North Carolina.";i:56;s:50:"Take a seat get ready for a dance fitness workout.";i:57;s:84:"By utilizing a chair this Zumba class provides a low-impact option good for seniors.";i:58;s:103:"The class will feature seated movements that help to improve balance coordination and overall strength.";i:59;s:66:"Feb 5 2018 - Explore Sallie Greens board Chair zumba on Pinterest.";i:60;s:51:"See more ideas about zumba workout videos exercise.";}}